SEARCH
Package org.example

Class Main

java.lang.Object
org.example.Main
public class Main extends Object
Main class to demonstrate the functionality of the ElectricAppliance hierarchy and the CustomApplianceSet collection. The main method is broken down into smaller, logical functions for better readability and modularity.
